summary: Currently, I am continuing my studies in Chemical Engineering as a Master student at the Politecnico di Milano after working in the chemical industry at Utility Support Group (USG). During my bachelors at TU/e and during my time at student team SOLID, I have discovered a great passion towards sustainable chemical technologies. Indeed, during the masters degree at Polimi, my knowledge in chemical engineering will be expanded and a specialisation track in Chemical Process Technologie (Process Design) will prepare me to work in the industrial field of chemistry while gaining knowledge on sustainable and innovative methods. I hope that I can help the world take a step towards a greener future with the knowledge and experiences I wish to gain.
